messages.content: I need EMS, don't hang up, sir.
You have reached the fire and EMS departments. All of our representatives are currently handling another emergency call.
Stay on the line, ma'am. I'm getting EMS for you.
Oh my God, what do we do?
Stay on the line. Help is on the way.
All of our agents are currently assisting other calls of emergency. Please continue to hold.
He's still seizing, we need help now.
Hold on, ma'am. I'm getting EMS for you. Do not hang up.
Hello, ma'am? Are you still there?
Okay, it looks like she hung up. She said there was somebody seizing at 8602 Cinnamon Creek, Apartment 709.
Do you need the phone number? It came across.
I'll have a unit dispatched right away.
